flowchart TD
  A[Authorized source inventory + hash] --> B[Text/image extraction]
  B --> C[Domain and trust-tier classification]
  C --> D[Candidate claim/card extraction]
  D --> E[Deterministic lint and schema validation]
  E --> F[Official-source comparison]
  F --> G{Conflict or high risk?}
  G -- yes --> H[Pharmacist adjudication]
  G -- no --> I[Pharmacist review]
  H --> I
  I --> J{All publication gates pass?}
  J -- no --> K[Quarantine or revise]
  J -- yes --> L[Compile immutable signed pack]
  L --> M[Golden tests + latency benchmark]
  M --> N{Release gate pass?}
  N -- no --> K
  N -- yes --> O[Publish version]
  O --> P[Monitor expiry, label changes, incidents]
  P --> Q[Stale/retire/rollback]
